Title: Inventory plugin and mk_inventory agent plugin feature for Linux block devices
Class: feature
Compatible: compat
Component: inv
Date: 1593590286
Edition: cre
Knowledge: undoc
Level: 1
Version: 2.0.0i1

{{mk_inventory}} now writes a section {{<<<lnx_block_devices>>>}} block device
information collected from system device tree.
{{lnx_block_devices}} inventory plugin extends the sites inventory section
{{Hardware/Storage/Block Devices}} with the collected information.
Current items are {{Disk ID}}, {{Filesystem Node}}, {{Firmware}},
{{Product}}, {{Serial Number}}, {{Size}} and {{Vendor}}.
